{"tid":1471391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"革命係要改變遊戲規則","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:34:12.000Z","uid":284645,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ae07055d5ef2ad2c8fa972ab4b4f03ae70b397","tid":1471391,"uid":284645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再撚叫人學政府同黑警</span></span>既手段，話乜乜革命是骯髒的、無條件撑乜乜的。依啲手段係港共、黑警既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲規則</span></span>、我哋革命唔係要改變依啲規咩？我哋幾時加入返佢地同佢地玩返同一套<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲規則</span></span>架？<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>盲撑、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>不割蓆得黎係會自我檢討進化架嘛<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>記者會鳩嗡、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>做文宣係唔會鳩嗡的<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>放鬼入黎、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>可以將之前衝突既責任推曬比佢哋<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>出黑暴警暴、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>係以武制暴<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>反人道、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>sell人道主義<br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>寸步不讓、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>之前點都set個deadline比佢，叫做比足機會佢先再升級架<br />\n7. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋</span>由立法會搶劫、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋</span>係自發衆籌的"},{"pid":"49e9c414a19aabd77b6539c953202626ea39aeae","tid":1471391,"uid":284645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3ae07055d5ef2ad2c8fa972ab4b4f03ae70b397","tid":1471391,"uid":284645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再撚叫人學政府同黑警</span></span>既手段，話乜乜革命是骯髒的、無條件撑乜乜的。依啲手段係港共、黑警既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲規